Included here is a prototype layout for a controller circuit.
This controller circuit is identical to the Controller.brd 
with the exception that the Laser is driven with 12V, not 5V.

-- Beta warning: this has not jet been fully tested by me.

Controller_v1.brd
--------------
  The layout source file

Controller_v1.sch
--------------
  The schematic source file.

  Controller_v1.hpgl, Controller_v1.ps
--------------------------------------
  Exported layout formats of the above board

Controller_v1.hpgl.nc
---------------------
  A g-code sample file that will produce a plot of the above
  board using the included board and firmware.